channel.title: {$}[PI]Webclient Help[PI]{$}
channel.description:
I need help making my Project Insanity Client a webclient. It apparently has problems getting connected to the cache. I am offering a cash reward via PayPal for whoever can fix the client and make it work 100%. You can either:
1. Take my client with the error, but everything else webclient related is done on it.
2. Take my client fresh, without the webclient coding, and make it from there.
I am offering around $5-$10, depending on how you help me and how fast you help me. Add me on MSN or Skype:
MSN - tormentedconnor@live.com Skype - lystuya
